CRYPTOGRAPHIC SOFTWARE NOTICE

This software contains cryptographic functionality. Export, re-export, or 
import of this software may be subject to legal restrictions in your 
jurisdiction.

The cryptographic implementations in this software use standard algorithms
(X25519, Ed25519, ChaCha20-Poly1305, BLAKE2b) via the Python cryptography
library, which uses OpenSSL as its backend.

This software is intended for legitimate privacy and communication purposes.
The authors do not condone its use for any illegal activities.
